## Grammar

- Qal perfect 3rd person masculine singular verbs
- Qal perfect 3rd person masculine plural verbs  
- Simple coordination with ו (vav)
- Basic word order: Verb-Subject-Object
- Definite article ה
- Simple prepositions (אֶל, מִן, לְ)
- Masculine singular nouns with definite article
- Basic adjective-noun agreement
- Direct speech introduction with אָמַר
- Simple adverbial expressions
